/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49feadee3018e51eb64397637de47abf0ea1c35e","tid":7202,"uid":25373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:48:19.000Z","msg":"入咗機門開始要苦行埋位，以示尊敬"},{"pid":"6220ed865e7eb6f1509bd07bdfafc53917d12573","tid":7202,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:48:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實地勤咩情況下幫你升級商務架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真，比錢比分以外<br />\n基本上得兩個可能，隻機經濟倉超賣，就要擺人上商務倉，不過都要排次序，高級會員開始排，跟住到staff 再到non member<br />\n第2 就係本身係會員，有時可能生日，可能入會週年等等，不過marketing 去抽/決定<br />\n地勤&quot;負責&quot;都係&quot;通知&quot;你only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 長知識了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815d79370f69be31c3048da76c33fac9898531a6","tid":7202,"uid":16383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:49:21.000Z","msg":"上千尋down定幾套動漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3126c5e72521634da14f9203f5328e769573ba51","tid":7202,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:50:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實地勤咩情況下幫你升級商務架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你諗多左啦，坐幾十次都唔會有一次發生喺你身上。<br />\n因為首先要班機econ位爆哂（即係幾乎無人no show）<br />\n然後得business仲有位先會upgrade你上去<br />\n而First class就唔清楚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：睇高登睇返嚟 自己無upgrade經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1d85e60eea0d8d9667b18b56b1f897c63e295b","tid":7202,"uid":31504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:53:16.000Z","msg":"咪撚叫杯面同咖啡！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad342fecc35c7c70a687f34be3089af3988047f8","tid":7202,"uid":14829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:53:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同隔離位好熟咁say hi <br />\n外國人多數叫呀jack 十成九都無錯<br />\n坐低就前後左右say 個hi <br />\nHi jack,佢就會好禮貌咁叫空姐請你去同機長傾計<br />\n仲會有機會上頭等!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9df60a5a9c7e91f3f2bd34f4115e8f51c6f01c","tid":7202,"uid":8680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:53:39.000Z","msg":"快過人訓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c670f60e4653e1359d362a72241147ec5c898be6","tid":7202,"uid":88,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36PYEP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36PYEP.jpg&h=d6807cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪話我唔提你 <br />\n想上機有得訓既 好快手淘呢個野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n包保你上機 訓到落機"},{"pid":"2f4eeaadcf6accd3f9cd2d5016b0f540803f4737","tid":7202,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:55:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實地勤咩情況下幫你升級商務架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真，比錢比分以外<br />\n基本上得兩個可能，隻機經濟倉超賣，就要擺人上商務倉，不過都要排次序，高級會員開始排，跟住到staff 再到non member<br />\n第2 就係本身係會員，有時可能生日，可能入會週年等等，不過marketing 去抽/決定<br />\n地勤&quot;負責&quot;都係&quot;通知&quot;你only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補充少少先 基本上可以話全部airline都會超賣<br />\n因為每架機都會有幾個passengers no show<br />\n所以airline會overbooking嚟保障返自己利益<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：major in tourism"},{"pid":"36a71d2d54fdac01735aaa7b310cd4ca4736edbe","tid":7202,"uid":27010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:56:00.000Z","msg":"借個post一問，點先可以唔會耳痛<br />\n第一次搭飛去日本痛到我仆街，諗住第二次去台灣時間短會好d，點知都係痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5f21c8edc700d900517954b86619ddfc92b205","tid":7202,"uid":88,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:57:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借個post一問，點先可以唔會耳痛<br />\n第一次搭飛去日本痛到我仆街，諗住第二次去台灣時間短會好d，點知都係痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香口膠 <br />\n都唔得既話 你天生耳膜薄<br />\n要睇西醫"},{"pid":"c358660670b64a6cc8ce27321ca0b6828bd68212","tid":7202,"uid":6424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T19:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實地勤咩情況下幫你升級商務架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真，比錢比分以外<br />\n基本上得兩個可能，隻機經濟倉超賣，就要擺人上商務倉，不過都要排次序，高級會員開始排，跟住到staff 再到non member<br />\n第2 就係本身係會員，有時可能生日，可能入會週年等等，不過marketing 去抽/決定<br />\n地勤&quot;負責&quot;都係&quot;通知&quot;你only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補充少少先 基本上可以話全部airline都會超賣<br />\n因為每架機都會有幾個passengers no show<br />\n所以airline會overbooking嚟保障返自己利益<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：major in tourism</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講就係咁講，<br />\n但係超賣依樣野，超賣幾多係一個問題，幾多班又係一個問題。<br />\n一班機超賣一隻同超賣十隻差好遠，10班機有1班機超賣同10班有8班都超賣又差好遠。<br />\n<br />\n公司做生意當然要保障利益，但事實係有d 航空公司計過數，用正價飛賺嘅錢賠比d cheap 飛賺差價賺到盡。<br />\n<br />\n利申，job in airline"}]}